### GET alle actieve marktplaats advertenties
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings

###

### POST een skin te koop
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": "6a11abbbc50b6fdeedc2829d", 
    "price": 350,
    "skinData": {
        "name": "Glacier",
        "weaponType": "Assault Rifle",
        "rarity": "Epic",
        "releaseSeason": "Operation Black Ice"
    }
}